text: Gilles Cocquempot (born October 22, 1952 in Éperlecques) is a member of the National Assembly of France. He represents the Pas-de-Calais department, and is a member of the Socialiste, radical, citoyen et divers gauche. ==References== Category:1952 births Category:Living people Category:People from Pas-de-Calais Category:Politicians from Hauts-de-France Category:Socialist Party (France) politicians Category:Deputies of the 11th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:Deputies of the 12th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:Deputies of the 13th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic
title: Gilles Cocquempot
